This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a new algorithm to improve the learning speed of contextual bandit algorithms. It also involves the use of conversational feedback, which can be related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the use of key-terms and categories can be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
